{"tid":307840,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃台仰打定輸數　預告明年中坐監","createTime":"2017-07-03T16:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T15:43:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"944f9f73f2cb507b61ae227d639b29b225d63d9f","tid":307840,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10154729872546696&amp;id=715826695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10154729872546696%26id%3D715826695&d=h1MB3VLklj48%2BH4sCaN85cVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=9fb2acfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10154729872546696&amp;id=715826695</a><br />\n<br />\n去年農曆新年爆發的旺角暴亂，本土民主前線黃台仰、梁天琦及另外8名男子，分別被控參與及煽動暴動等罪，法庭將案件定於8月7日預審，明年1月中至5月中於高等法院正式開審，預計審訊80天。<br />\n<br />\n黃台仰最近接受台灣傳媒訪問時打定輸數，預告於明年中「就會入獄了」，又指由於外界認定他為該次行動的領袖，加上早前多名青年被控暴動罪成，判處入獄最少3年，暗示自己不被重判的機會很微。"},{"pid":"b9906e6aab22e0e8cf8a57b826570fde41048344","tid":307840,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:07:52.000Z","msg":"真係打唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b63e3da05a58c34afa9ea147f09c12bbeda4c0","tid":307840,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:28:32.000Z","msg":"但係本土派只係互屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c099b409f42dd784fa321455dc0b297de340702c","tid":307840,"uid":39855,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"有台仰先有魚革！相信佢架人會等佢出來。<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/04/002822_ee1466ac88bf66250fd7f853626ec7a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F04%2F002822_ee1466ac88bf66250fd7f853626ec7a6.jpg&h=e25e8f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eaca901018a506ad2317e2ec137c003960d012d9","tid":307840,"uid":79563,